   version stable 4.10 4.9 4.8
  category archive
 attribute console
    source $GNU_URL sharutils/sharutils-$VERSION.tar.bz2
  homepage http://www.gnu.org/software/sharutils/sharutils.html
      opts --with-gnu-gettext
  estimate 1500
# May have an optional requirement on gmime
      desc 'creates shell archives for transmission by email
sharutils shell archives out of many files, preparing
them for transmission by electronic mail services.
A shell archive is a collection of files that can
be unpacked by /bin/sh.
Shar may compress files, uuencode binary files,
split long files and construct multi-part mailings,
ensure correct unsharing order, and provide simplistic checksums.
Also contains uudecode and uuencode.'
